HEADWORD: Abusiveness
<hw>A*bu"sive*ness</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The quality of being
abusive; rudeness of language, or violence to the person.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Pick out mirth, like stones out of thy ground,⟦br⟧
Profaneness, filthiness, <qex>abusiveness</qex>.</q>
<rj><qau>Herbert.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

